+section
  +heading2.mb-1 Buttons
  +paragraph.mb-8 Use buttons for actions in forms, dialogs, and more with support for multiple sizes, states, and more.

  +heading3.mb-8 Buttons
  +example.mb-8
    +exampleDisplay
      +button(kind="primary") Primary Button
      +button(kind="secondary") Secondary Button
      +button(kind="ghost") Ghost Button
      +button(kind="critical") Critical Button
