      +button(kind="primary") Primary Button
      +button(kind="secondary") Secondary Button
      +button(kind="ghost") Ghost Button
      +button(kind="critical") Critical Button

  +heading4.mb-1 Shorthands
  +paragraph.mb-8 Use the button shorthands to create Primary, Secondary, Ghost and Critical buttons.

  +example.mb-8
    +exampleDisplay
      +primaryButton Primary Button
      +secondaryButton Secondary Button
      +ghostButton Ghost Button
      +criticalButton Critical Button
